# {project_name}

An ADHD Framework project.

## Quick Start

### Prerequisites

- Python 3.11+
- [UV](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/) package manager

### Setup

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone <your-repo-url>
cd {project_name}

# Install dependencies and sync workspace
uv sync

# Run the framework CLI
uv run adhd --help
```

## Project Structure

```
{project_name}/
├── modules/
│   ├── foundation/   # Bootstrap modules (config, logging)
│   ├── runtime/      # Production application modules
│   └── dev/          # Development-only tools
├── project/          # Project-specific data
├── tests/            # Test files
├── app.py            # Application entry point
└── pyproject.toml    # Project configuration
```

## Development

```bash
# Add a new module
uv run adhd new-module

# Refresh framework (sync instructions, etc.)
uv run adhd refresh

# Run tests
uv run pytest
```

